data.description: LOWER PAYMENT! Seller offering to BUY DOWN Buyers Interest Rate by 2% 1st Year & 1% 2nd Year! Enjoy all there is at LAKE ST LOUIS COMMUNITY ASSOCIATION! Feel like you’re on VACATION everyday w/ Amenities & Lake Rights! Move In 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath, 2 Car 26’ Extra Deep Garage! Over 2000 Finished Sq Ft! UPDATES GALORE! BEAUTIFUL Engineered Wood Plank & Vinyl Plank Floors thruout! Enjoy cozy nights by the Fireplace in the HUGE Great Room! Kitchen w/ GRANITE Counters, 42” Wood Cabinets, Cabinet Pantry, S/S Appliances, 5 Burner Gas Range & Refrig stays! Open Dining Room & Mid Floor OVERSIZED Laundry. Owners Suite w/ Adult Height Granite Vanity, Designer Tile Shower & Opening Window! Beds 2 & 3 share the Freestanding Tub/Shower, Oversized Adult Height Granite Vanity & Opening Window! Lower Level offers Recreation, Bonus Room & STORAGE. Level Backyard w/ Full-Length Patio & Invisible Pet Fence! WELL MAINTAINED! Newer Roof, Windows, HVAC & more! WENTZVILLE SCHOOLS!
